#-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  atom_colours.dat
#  ----------------
#
#  This file lists the X11 colour names of (most) of the atoms which may be 
#  found in PDB files.
#
#  Format:  Residue-name Atom-name  X11-colour-name
#
#  NB. a residue name of "UNK" acts as a catch-all. Most atoms are coloured
#  using this mapping, although individual atoms of a residue may be coloured
#  explicitly with this syntax.
#
